    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A mixture of naturally occuring mineral material used by the Maya in the preparation of plasters and mortars. It has been employed as a building and paving material in Mesoamerica since antiquity.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
